             having two Indictments against them both for <rs id="t16761011-3-off9" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16761011-3-off9" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16761011-3-off9" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               felonious taking the Goods of two 
